1
00:00:52,759 --> 00:00:53,960
Lu Qi is your daughter too.

2
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:56,159
You don't care about her at all.

3
00:00:56,159 --> 00:00:57,359
What's there to care about her?

4
00:00:57,719 --> 00:00:59,240
What if I were the one lying here?

5
00:00:59,560 --> 00:01:00,439
Would you have done anything differently?

6
00:01:00,960 --> 00:01:02,000
Would you have shot me too?

7
00:01:11,159 --> 00:01:11,840
Jiang Yue,

8
00:01:13,439 --> 00:01:14,480
ask yourself,

9
00:01:15,680 --> 00:01:17,120
do you even see me as your father anymore?

10
00:01:17,719 --> 00:01:19,319
The company is in such a big crisis now.

11
00:01:20,079 --> 00:01:22,000
Our Jiang family's decades-long legacy

12
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:22,879
is about to be ruined.

13
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:24,640
Ask yourself,

14
00:01:26,480 --> 00:01:28,040
if you hadn't gone against me,

15
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:30,959
how could they have taken advantage?

16
00:01:38,560 --> 00:01:39,920
I've always wondered

17
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:42,719
why you wanted to shoot Lu Qi.

18
00:01:44,760 --> 00:01:46,319
After all, when she and her mother first came,

19
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:48,040
you asked me to protect Lu Qi.

20
00:01:49,599 --> 00:01:50,640
But now I understand.

21
00:01:52,439 --> 00:01:53,239
It's because she

22
00:01:54,439 --> 00:01:56,359
helped me break free from your control.

23
00:01:57,519 --> 00:01:59,439
Your real purpose is not to kill her,

24
00:02:00,599 --> 00:02:01,640
but to warn me.

25
00:02:02,719 --> 00:02:03,519
You want me

26
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:05,280
to go back on my knees,

27
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:07,400
begging you

28
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:08,719
to let her go.

29
00:02:10,199 --> 00:02:10,560
Right?

30
00:02:11,719 --> 00:02:12,759
If you go with me now,

31
00:02:13,719 --> 00:02:15,319
I can pretend nothing happened.

32
00:02:16,080 --> 00:02:17,759
But it has already happened.

33
00:02:22,439 --> 00:02:23,080
Do you believe that

34
00:02:23,080 --> 00:02:24,080
even if she wakes up,

35
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:25,319
I can still kill her?

36
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:25,800
Yes.

37
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:27,759
I do.

38
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:30,479
I was six when my mother died.

39
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:33,479
I couldn't protect her back then,

40
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:36,960
but now I can.

41
00:02:37,919 --> 00:02:39,000
From now on,

42
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:42,400
I'll never leave Lu Qi's side

43
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:44,439
until she recovers.

44
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:47,919
You're still acting on emotions.

45
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:51,400
All my teaching was in vain.

46
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:52,960
You're unworthy of being human,

47
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,280
treating lives as grass.

48
00:02:56,719 --> 00:02:57,360
You don't need to learn.

49
00:03:05,879 --> 00:03:06,479
In your heart,

50
00:03:06,479 --> 00:03:07,680
that's all I taught you, isn't it?

51
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:08,639
Jiang Yue,

52
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:09,960
without me,

53
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:10,719
how could you

54
00:03:10,719 --> 00:03:12,280
grow up so privileged?

55
00:03:13,039 --> 00:03:14,120
I grew up in comfort?

56
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:16,360
When you trained me as a child,

57
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:17,439
did you ever care about my life?

58
00:03:18,120 --> 00:03:19,000
I had no childhood,

59
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:20,240
no hobbies.

60
00:03:21,080 --> 00:03:22,719
As long as something could attract my attention,

61
00:03:22,719 --> 00:03:23,680
you would destroy it.

62
00:03:24,759 --> 00:03:26,520
I had to devote myself to you

63
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:28,319
to carry out your so-called mission.

64
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:29,759
Jiang Yue

65
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:32,639
Don't take credit for what you didn't do.

66
00:03:32,639 --> 00:03:33,840
You chose this.

67
00:03:34,599 --> 00:03:35,280
Is it for me?

68
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:39,479
Everything you do is for your mother.

69
00:03:40,159 --> 00:03:41,240
Only at this time,

70
00:03:42,639 --> 00:03:44,120
you would mention my mother.

71
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:51,240
My mother has been dead for 16 years.

72
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:53,520
You always tell me

73
00:03:54,439 --> 00:03:55,759
that Black Snow killed her.

74
00:03:57,439 --> 00:03:58,400
Look into my eyes.

75
00:04:00,039 --> 00:04:00,800
Is it true?

76
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:01,800
Then tell me,

77
00:04:01,879 --> 00:04:02,919
if it's not the black snow, who is it?

78
00:04:03,159 --> 00:04:04,120
Is it true?

79
00:04:15,199 --> 00:04:16,519
Sir, let's go.

80
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:20,480
You're crazy.

81
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:22,680
You're really crazy.

82
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:00,439
How is it?

83
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:01,439
Has Qi Qi woken up?

84
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:05,879
I've asked the doctor.

85
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:07,720
Qi Qi's eyes are not seriously injured.

86
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:09,240
With proper treatment, she can recover.

87
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:11,160
Qi Qi's accident

88
00:05:12,199 --> 00:05:13,399
is related to you.

89
00:05:14,319 --> 00:05:15,879
Whoever did it should take responsibility.

90
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:16,959
Don't wrong me.

91
00:05:16,959 --> 00:05:17,759
Jiang Yue,

92
00:05:18,639 --> 00:05:20,040
you deal with Jiang Changfa yourself.

93
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:22,519
I'll take care of the rest.

94
00:05:32,439 --> 00:05:32,959
Qi Qi,

95
00:05:34,399 --> 00:05:34,800
I'm here.

96
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:40,560
I can't see, Jiang Yue.

97
00:05:48,199 --> 00:05:48,920
What is this?

98
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:52,560
Is this so-called love?

99
00:06:02,839 --> 00:06:03,879
If you help me destroy this exhibition,

100
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:05,920
how much do you want?

101
00:06:06,879 --> 00:06:07,519
I'll give you all.

102
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:12,879
Once 3Z falls,

103
00:06:13,319 --> 00:06:15,319
it will be much smoother for us

104
00:06:15,399 --> 00:06:16,600
to cooperate with those foreigners.

105
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:19,560
3Z is now like a grasshopper in autumn.

106
00:06:20,319 --> 00:06:21,560
They can't jump anymore.

107
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:23,759
Don't underestimate Jiang Changfa.

108
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:25,199
But it doesn't matter.

109
00:06:25,959 --> 00:06:26,959
We still have the Butterfly.

110
00:06:27,879 --> 00:06:29,160
He should be taking action soon.

111
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:49,079
Butterfly.

112
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:52,000
You were originally the one who set up the game,

113
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:54,600
yet now you're

114
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:56,000
working for the pieces,

115
00:06:57,639 --> 00:06:59,079
and you seem to enjoy it.

116
00:07:01,399 --> 00:07:02,360
I don't understand,

117
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:05,240
but I know one thing for sure,

118
00:07:06,639 --> 00:07:07,560
at least right now,

119
00:07:09,199 --> 00:07:09,839
I'm very happy.

120
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:02,920
Jiang Yue.

121
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:04,519
I'm here.

122
00:08:04,639 --> 00:08:05,439
Jiang Yue.

123
00:08:06,079 --> 00:08:07,000
Are you hurt?

124
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:08,160
I'm fine.

125
00:08:10,319 --> 00:08:11,319
Do you feel sick?

126
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:12,720
No.

127
00:08:15,519 --> 00:08:16,000
Jiang Yue.

128
00:08:16,879 --> 00:08:18,160
Let's go out for a walk.

129
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:19,360
Okay.

130
00:08:27,399 --> 00:08:27,959
I'm sorry.

131
00:08:30,079 --> 00:08:30,519
It's okay.

132
00:08:31,319 --> 00:08:32,159
It's not your fault.

133
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:46,600
Auntie.

134
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:48,360
Yue'er,

135
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:50,639
I saw on the news that the exhibition was in trouble.

136
00:08:51,039 --> 00:08:51,919
Changfa didn't let me go there.

137
00:08:51,919 --> 00:08:53,000
Qi Qi didn't answer my phone.

138
00:08:53,399 --> 00:08:54,360
How are you now?

139
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:55,240
Are you hurt?

140
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:58,080
Mom, we're fine.

141
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:00,000
Well,

142
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,960
I'm busy now. I have to go.

143
00:09:03,919 --> 00:09:04,200
Bye.

144
00:09:18,120 --> 00:09:18,679
Jiang Yue,

145
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:20,960
I will get better.

146
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:23,840
Let's go.

147
00:09:38,159 --> 00:09:38,759
Where's Jiang Yue?

148
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:40,559
He's in the hospital.

149
00:09:43,120 --> 00:09:43,559
Sir,

150
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:45,279
the murderer this time

151
00:09:46,120 --> 00:09:47,399
was hired by Wang Yuhe

152
00:09:47,399 --> 00:09:48,559
of Black Snow.

153
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:51,000
Wang Yuhe.

154
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:55,360
What a disappointment.

155
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:58,519
And we also found out who cut off Zone D.

156
00:09:58,960 --> 00:09:59,679
It's also Wang Yuhe.

157
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:04,120
This is a surprise.

158
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:06,320
Sir.

159
00:10:07,159 --> 00:10:07,919
Wang Yuhe

160
00:10:08,360 --> 00:10:09,840
shouldn't know Zone D is ours.

161
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:11,759
Otherwise, why would he

162
00:10:11,759 --> 00:10:12,639
to sabotage the exhibition

163
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:14,080
instead of taking down us?

164
00:10:15,799 --> 00:10:16,559
If it's exposed,

165
00:10:17,720 --> 00:10:18,759
3Z will be at risk.

166
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:21,759
We have to hold on to District 45

167
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:23,279
to give the boss an explanation.

168
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:24,679
Well.

169
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:27,000
Go to the hospital again

170
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:29,600
and ask Jiang Yue to meet me at 11:00 tomorrow.

171
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:32,240
Okay.

172
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:45,799
Hello,

173
00:10:46,559 --> 00:10:47,159
I'm Chu Mo.

174
00:10:51,799 --> 00:10:53,600
If you like to get wet, do it yourself.

175
00:10:54,200 --> 00:10:54,679
Come home with me.

176
00:10:55,159 --> 00:10:55,799
Jiang Yue,

177
00:11:29,240 --> 00:11:29,799
do you like her?

178
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:30,679
Yes.

179
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:33,000
Do you like her as a man likes a woman?
